    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for Model Risk Level 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 for Class II devices at MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the CPB device, with the relative hemolysis index prediction error within the 15% acceptance threshold across all five operating points. The credibility evidence package satisfies project requirements for regulatory submission support. The UnitOfAssurance is accepted under the Minimal profile binding.",
